  "title": "*New* Healthcare Operations Executive (Office Hours, 5 Days) #HJG",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Support the Operations team in project management and administrative tasks for clinical departments.</p></li><li><p>Assist in planning, financial and budgetary assessment, and execution of assigned projects.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with clinical, nursing, facilities, and other operational stakeholders to ensure smooth project progress.</p></li><li><p>Prepare timely status updates and reports for ongoing projects.</p></li><li><p>Provide secretariat support for committees related to assigned projects.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bachelor’s Degree in any discipline</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, PowerPoint)</p></li><li><p>Able to start work immediately</p></li></ul><p><strong></strong><br />If you are interested in this position, do kindly drop your most updated resume to <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">joshua.gan@recruitexpress.com.sg</a> and <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">leonleong@recruitexpress.com.sg</a> (Attn: Operations Executive)<br />Leon Leong De Cong<br />R1551708<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifesciences Division)<br />EA License: 99C4599</p>",
